<h3 id="building--programming">Building &amp; Programming</h3>

<p>The launching mechanism was a half gear which, via a geared winch and fishing line, loaded a spring inside the barrel and pulled back the piston and ball-carriage.</p>

<video id="vid" style="width: 100%; max-width: 600px;" preload="auto" muted="muted" loop="loop" autoplay="autoplay">
